        <title>Mobile Service Plugins for Xamarin.Forms</title>
        <description>
Includes several essentials services for development with Xamarin.Forms
- Camera
- Photo Gallery Access
- Device Information
- Network Detection and Monitoring
- Geolocation
- Settings
- Phone Initiation
- SMS Initiation
- Text-to-Speech
- File System Management
